<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Homepage</title>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-4 fade" style="padding-top: 100px;">
            <div class="mission">
                <h1>Our Mission</h1>
                <p>An app that allows local artists to lease their artwork to clients, on a monthly or yearly basis. </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4">
            <div class="bodyofIndex">
                <div class="slideshow">
                    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                        <div class="signupButton">
                            <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg active animated wobble" role="button" aria-pressed="true">Sign Up Now</a>
                        </div>
                        <br>
                        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                        </ol>
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="./images/determination-priscilla-jo.jpg" alt="First slide">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="./images/never-alone-by-sharon-cummings-sharon-cummings.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img class="d-block w-100" src="./images/LOVE-BY-THE-PALETTE.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                        </a>
                        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
                <div class="col-4 fade" style="padding-top: 100px;">
                    <div class="instructions">
                        <h1>How to use the app</h1>
                        <ol>
                            <li>The first step is to create an account.</li>
                            <li>Make sure to specify the type of account, either artist or customer.</li>
                            <li>Then, if you registered an artist account, you can list paintings by clicking the "post" tab</li>
                            <li>Lastly, we can view the database of all paintings under the "listings" tab </li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>